My easy peasy lemon squeezy Summer Makeup Routine ☀️👀🫶🏻

Thots-
1. 10/10 would recommend the @maybelline 3 in 1 (it isnt available in India though🥲)
2. Less is more, only apply product where you need the coverage to avoid a heavy/ cakey base! 
3. Don’t over powder your face (a mistake alot of people make during summers) which only ends up making your makeup look like plaster due to the sweat 
4. Spf before & a good setting spray after is a must
5. Ummm…idk whatelse?! Drink yo wotahh🧊
